name: Cyrce's Circlet
description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description:
Equip: Your harmful attacks and abilities have a high chance to build momentum, granting 2% bonus movement speed per stack.

At 5 stacks you reach full momentum increasing your movement speed bonus to 20% for 10 sec. While at full momentum, your attacks hit the target at high velocity dealing an additional 40,585 Nature damage scaling up with your current movement speed.
Equip: Your harmful spells and abilities apply Ratfang Toxin to your target, stacking up to 5 times.
Use: Release all toxin stacks to deal 776,744 Nature damage, plus 88,771 per stack over 5 sec. (1 Min 30 Sec Cooldown)

Equip: Gain Ascendance every 8 seconds spent in combat.

Ascendance grants 89 of a random secondary stat for 15 sec, stacking up to 10 times.

This is a Nerubian embellishment.
